              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The R-Matrix analysis performed with the code",
                "MINRMATRIX indicates that a good fit can be achieved",
                "by including a 1/2+ resonance with c.m. energy E =",
                "2.45(1) MeV and a 5/2+ resonance with c.m. energy E =",
                "4.15(6) MeV. This fit has four free parameters: the",
                "c.m. energies and the spectroscopic factors for the",
                "two states. Only two channels were used in the fit:",
                "the isospin-allowed proton and neutron decays."
